                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card border-0">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="text-center pb-3"><img src="~/Images/ResearchWorldWide/02-icon.png" alt=""></div>
                            <h3 class="card-title text-center title-success text-uppercase">Stay Connected </h3>
                            <p class="card-text pt-2">
